14 SUMMARY
1155 This amendment removes provisions in the bill that change the costs related to public
1166 safety improvements that are considered authorized project costs and that provide for the
1177 retention or return of tax increment revenues remaining in an affordable housing
1188 development fund on the date a development district ends.
